caption.title: DENV2 infection in the reproductive tract of male mosquito progeny (E2-F1) of infected GDLS female.
caption.p: DENV2 E antigen was detected in testis and peripheral tissue of accessory glands by IFA using DENV2 specific 3H5 monoclonal antibody. A. Reproductive tract of male mosquito progeny (E2-10d-F1) from DENV2 infected GDLS female. B. Reproductive tract of male mosquito progeny from GDLS non-infected female.
